unittitle_ssm: Records of the Office of Media Production
abstract_ssm: The Office of Media Production was established to create digital communication strategies to advance recruitment, development and public relations. This collection of recordings include promotional material, commencement footage and documentary footage of speakers, visitors and events. Tapes range in date from 1983 to 2010.
